<span class="copy_header">For Students</span><br>
The lessons below have been developed as classroom activities, to be completed with the help of your teacher. The lessons are not recommended for use by individual students.

<br><br>

<a href="../classroomActivities/8-12_intro.html">Reconstructing History: The Wright Brothers'<br>First Flight >></a><br>
<br>
<a href="../classroomActivities/4-7_intro.cfm">Wright Brothers Biography: An Illustrated <br>Timeline  >></a><br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:openFlashPage()">Airplane Anatomy: Helping Orville and Wilbur Assemble the 1903 Flyer >></a><br>
This is an interactive activity. If you are using a dial-up connection, please be patient while the activity loads. It may take up to four minutes.




